{"tid":2322917,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅幫他伴舞、2PM送親筆信！陸男星：我是第一個在JYP培訓的","createTime":"2020-12-12T17:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T18:22:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"03df378f84400f7c397c901c5d127ace9f94c99c","tid":2322917,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"大陸選秀節目《追光吧哥哥》開播，台灣觀眾熟知的明道、汪東城、胡夏等藝人皆有參與演出，成功帶起不少話題。其中男星劉維出場時說到，「我是第一個在JYP培訓的人」，還被網友翻出「小野馬」泫雅為他伴舞的影片，引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5331/5331125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5331%2F5331125.jpg&h=41786006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲劉維曾在JYP培訓，泫雅、2PM都曾和他同框。（圖／翻攝自微博／劉維）<br />\n<br />\n劉維2006年曾到韓國JYP經紀公司進行培訓，時間長達半年，在當地發表了個人歌曲、登台演出。結束後回到家鄉繼續發展，陸續和王祖藍、范曉萱等人有過合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5331/5331121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5331%2F5331121.jpg&h=c5326efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲劉維在節目發言。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n自認「唱跳界的遺珠之憾」，劉維想要透過舞台讓大家知道自己是誰，更在微博PO文，「就像在JYP練習時收獲的寄語，我希望成為一個Superstar，這個心願從未改變」展現決心，配圖則放上和韓團2PM成員的合照，還有玉澤演、Nichkhun寫給他的親筆信，看得出感情相當好。另外有網友挖出他在韓國表演時，身邊伴舞竟是「性感小野馬」泫雅，影片曝光讓網友大呼意外，也大讚劉維的唱跳實力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5331/5331123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5331%2F5331123.jpg&h=87176981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼2PM親筆信。（圖／翻攝自微博／劉維）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5331/5331124.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5331%2F5331124.jpg&h=8dd26098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5331/5331126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5331%2F5331126.jpg&h=cff767e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泫雅曾擔任劉維伴舞。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5331/5331135.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5331%2F5331135.jpg&h=56037445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲劉維發文。（圖／翻攝自微博／劉維）"},{"pid":"309e0ec5fc4eb7ec4c8ff8371e3f1f63b372190a","tid":2322917,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T18:22:15.000Z","msg":"大陸仔"}]}